Sentencas: A cathode-supported tubular solid oxide fuel cell (CTSOFC) with the length of 6.0 cm and outside diameter of 1.0 cm has been successfully fabricated via dip-coating and co-sintering techniques.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of a cathode-supported tubular solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: A crack-free electrolyte film with a thickness of similar to 14 mu m was obtained by co-firing of cathode/cathode active layer/electrolyte/anode at 1250 degrees C.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of a cathode-supported tubular solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The relative low densifying temperature for electrolyte was attributed to the large shrinkage of the green tubular which assisted the densification of electrolyte.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of a cathode-supported tubular solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The assembled cell was electrochemically characterized with humidified H-2 as fuel and O-2 as oxidant.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of a cathode-supported tubular solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The open circuit voltages (OCV) were 1.1, 1.08 and 1.06V at 750, 800 and 850 degrees C, respectively, with the maximum power densities of 157, 272 and 358 mW cm(-2) at corresponding temperatures.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of a cathode-supported tubular solid oxide fuel cell
